to%20acknowledge%20that%20he's%20a%20%26quot%3Bpiece%20of%20trash%26quot%3B%20like%20everyone%20else%20who%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20games%2C%20the%20recruiter%20ends%20up%20with%20the%20last%20bullet%20in%20the%20gun%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20after%20Gi-hun%20calls%20him%20a%20dog%2C%20ddakji%20man%20pulls%20the%20trigger%2C%20ending%20his%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c433b01c-bebf-4c74-8498-f670aa6334e0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20more%20Mr.%20Nice%20Ddakji%20Guy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20one%2C%20the%20recruiter%20was%20an%20entrancing%20figure%20because%20of%20the%20difference%20in%20his%20demeanor%20(perfect%2C%20poised)%20and%20actions%20(slapping%20the%20daylights%20out%20of%20people).%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Hwang%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20not%20only%20reveal%20his%20backstory%2C%20but%20also%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20kind%20of%20state%20he%20is%20in%20as%20a%20human%20being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%3F%20One%20untethered%20to%20anything%20except%20his%20objectively%20wild%20and%20remarkably%20strong%20convictions.%20This%20is%20a%20man%20who%20does%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0harassing%20people%20already%20being%20crushed%20by%20debt%2C%20sentencing%20them%20to%20a%20death%20game%2C%20and%20murder%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20the%20love%20of%20the%20game.%20It's%20not%20really%20clear%20why%20he%20believes%20people%2C%20like%20those%20he%20recruits%20into%20the%20games%2C%20are%20trash.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20it's%20incredibly%20clear%20that%20he's%20a%20sadist%20who%20will%20play%20any%20game%20he%20initiates%20to%20the%20end%2C%20even%20if%20he%20has%20to%20forfeit%20his%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222571%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gong%20yoo%20and%20lee%20jung-jae%20in%20squid%20game.%20they're%20both%20middle%20aged%20men%2C%20sitting%20across%20from%20each%20other%20at%20a%20table%20in%20a%20warmly%20it%2C%20but%20mostly%20dark%20room.%20gong%2C%20as%20the%20recruiter%2C%20is%20holding%20a%20gun%20and%20leaning%20onto%20the%20table%20toward%20lee%2C%20who%20plays%20gi-hun%20and%20is%20sitting%20tensey%20on%20the%20other%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67661231a40fd2a95c0c2c7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221928%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGong%20Yoo%20and%20Lee%20Jung-jae%20as%20the%20recruiter%20and%20Gi-hun%20in%20season%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENo%20Ju-han%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGong%20brings%20a%20charged%20energy%20to%20his%20sequences%20in%20episode%20one%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20his%20confrontation%20with%20Gi-hun%20%E2%80%94%20that%20remains%20largely%20unmatched%20by%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20season.%20His%20physicality%2C%20whether%20it's%20getting%20up%20in%20another%20performer's%20space%20or%20spinning%20the%20barrel%20of%20a%20pistol%2C%20is%20unmatched.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGong%20Yoo%20is%20an%20actor%20who's%20mostly%20taken%20on%20very%20sweet%20characters%2C%26quot%3B%20Hwang%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20never%20done%20something%20that's%20as%20crazy%20or%20insane%20as%20this%20one%2C%20so%20I%20was%20personally%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20he%20was%20going%20to%20portray%20the%20character%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20one%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20recruiter%20was%20a%20tightly%20coiled%20spring.%20In%20season%20two%2C%20Hwang%20and%20Gong%20finally%20let%20him%20snap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20is%20now%20streaming%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-recruiter-ddakji-man-fate-squid-game-season-2-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735208641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6766109ba40fd2a95c0c2c68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22orig