able%20to%20credibly%20implement%20those%20ideas%20and%20principles%20as%20envisaged%2C%20especially%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20long%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20RAND%20warned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUkraine%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20contradictions%2C%20where%2021st-century%20technologies%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-fighting-sees-new-drone-warfare-hit-to-kill-interceptions-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edrones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20exist%20alongside%20artillery%20barrages%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-ukraine-russia-front-line-trenches-scenes-from-world-wars-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etrench%20warfare%20straight%20from%201917%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20While%20militaries%20want%20to%20learn%20the%20lessons%20for%20future%20wars%2C%20distinguishing%20what's%20old%20from%20what's%20new%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20are%20specific%20features%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20versus%20permanent%20trends%20%E2%80%94%20isn't%20easy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20what%20is%20the%20future%20of%20airpower%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-teaching-nato-air-forces-lessons-fighting-russia-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECrewed%20aircraft%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20had%20a%20surprisingly%20limited%20impact%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20as%20have%20helicopters.%20%26quot%3BThe%20deployment%20of%20%5Bground-based%20air%20defenses%5D%20has%20underscored%20the%20poor%20survivability%20of%20rotary-wing%20assets%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20with%20a%20reduced%20use%20of%20platforms%20including%20helicopters%20for%20tactical%20air%20mobility%20maneuvers%20and%20%5Bcasualty%20evacuation%5D%2C%20compared%20with%20operations%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%2C%26quot%3B%20RAND%20said.%20The%20sheer%20numbers%20and%20accuracy%20of%20air%20defenses%20like%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-giving-ukraine-second-patriot-missile-system-fight-russia-reports-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPatriot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Ukraine)%20or%20S-300%20and%20S-400s%20(Russia)%20force%20jets%20to%20fly%20at%20a%20remove%20from%20the%20battlefield%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20the%20battlefield's%20lines%20are%20largely%20static.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Royal%20Danish%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20fighters%20fly%20off%20the%20wing%20of%20a%20US%20Air%20Force%20B-52%20bomber%20in%20November.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757278adc8b666017f20b3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Danish%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20fighters%20fly%20off%20the%20wing%20of%20a%20US%20Air%20Force%20B-52%20bomber%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sgt.%20Emily%20Farnsworth%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20issues%20are%20hardly%20academic%20for%20NATO%20militaries.%20They%20operate%20the%20world's%20most%20numerous%20and%20advanced%20air%20forces%2C%20outgrowths%20from%20the%20Cold%20War%20strategy%20of%20using%20tactical%20airpower%20to%20stall%20and%20fracture%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20numerically%20superior%20ground%20forces.%20If%20their%20use%20is%20now%20much%20more%20limited%2C%20it%20suggests%20NATO%20armies%20will%20face%20a%20much%20more%20difficult%20ground%20fight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDrones%20have%20largely%20replaced%20crewed%20aircraft%20for%20reconnaissance%20and%20attack%20missions.%20And%2C%20small%2C%20expendable%20drones%20have%20replaced%20larger%20UAVs%20such%20as%20the%20Turkish-made%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturkeys-bayraktar-tb2-drones-ineffective-ukraine-war-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBayraktar%202%20strike%20drone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Ukraine%20used%20with%20devastating%20effect%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20war.%20Yet%20massive%20use%20of%20drones%20has%20failed%20to%20provide%20either%20side%20with%20victory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUkraine%20has%20tried%20to%20shed%20its%20Soviet-era%20doctrine%20in%20favor%20of%20Western-style%20maneuver%20warfare%2C%20with%20limited%20but%20not%20decisive%20success.%20Russia%20has%20used%20massive%20artillery%20barrages%20and%20human-wave%20assaults%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20tactics%20the%20Red%20Army%20used%20against%20the%20Germans%20in%20World%20War%20II%20%E2%80%94%20to%20achieve%20steady%20but%20incremental%20gains%20at%20ferocious%20cost%3B%20by%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sets-new-average-daily-losses-record-in-ukraine-uk-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20November%20was%20the%20highest%20month%20for%20Russian%20soldiers%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sets-new-average-daily-losses-record-in-ukraine-uk-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekilled%20and%20wounded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20entire%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20airpower%2C%20neither%20maneuver%20nor%20positional%20warfare%20have%20led%20to%20a%20decisive%20strategic%20outcome%2C%20but%20claims%20in%20the%20literature%20about%20the%20demise%20of%20such%20approaches%20are%20premature%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RAND.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20apparent%20neutralization%20of%20airpower%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20NATO.%20Western%20nations%20have%20tended%20to%20invest%20in%20aircraft%20rather%20than%20building%20huge%20numbers%20of%20artillery%20pieces%2C%20as%20Russia%20and%20China%20have%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERAND%20does%20see%20several%20enduring%20lessons%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20for%20NATO.%20One%20is%20having%20adequate%20quantities%20of%20personnel%20and%20material%20to%20absorb%20and%20replenish%20the%20constant%20drain%20of%20combat%20losses%20in%20a%20long%20war.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20efficiency%20afforded%20by%20new%20technology%20can%20offset%20the%20need%20for%20mass%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20it%20cannot%20replace%20the%20general%20need%20for%20mass.%20We%20have%20not%20yet%20observed%20any%20game-changing%20technology%20or%20tactic%20that%20negates%20the%20need%20for%20critical%20mass%20in%20personnel%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20materiel%20and%20stockpiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20issues%20are%20especially%20acute%20for%20the%20UK.%20The%20British%20Army%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-army-size-smallest-since-napoleonic-wars-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshrinking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%2072%2C000%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20the%20Napoleonic%20Wars%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20Royal%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%20are%20also%20a%20fraction%20of%20their%20Cold%20War%20strength.%20In%20the%20event%20of%20a%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20such%20as%20an%20invasion%20of%20Poland%20or%20Eastern%20Europe%2C%20the%20UK%20might%20barely%20be%20able%20to%20scrape%20together%20a%20full-strength%20mechanized%20division.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RAND%20study%20also%20examines%20how%20military%20power%20emerges%20from%20more%20than%20just%20weapons%20and%20strategy.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Kremlin's%20worst%20error%20was%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-russian-blunders-during-putin-war-against-ukraine-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunderestimate%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20government%20to%20preserve%20their%20independence%20as%20a%20nation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20war%20has%20re-emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20narrative%20and%20audience-centric%20approaches.%20This%20includes%20the%20crucial%20but%20often%20overlooked%20role%20of%20a%20national%20will%20to%20fight%20%E2%80%94%20a%20topic%20extensively%20analyzed%20at%20RAND%20but%20often%20overlooked%2C%20especially%20in%20Western%20defense%20establishments.%3Csup%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20lesson%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20is%20the%20importance%20of%20adaptability.%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20have%20proven%20rigid%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20but%20quite%20adaptable%20in%20others%2C%20such%20as%20mastering%20the%20use%20of%20drones.%20%26quot%3BTechnological%20trends%20towards%20automation%2C%20process%20optimization%20and%20a%20more%20transparent%2C%20networked%20and%20data-rich%20battlespace%20aside%2C%20the%20war%20has%20for%20example%20reiterated%20the%20enduring%20impact%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20friction%20in%20complicating%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20RAND%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20means%20NATO%20must%20constantly%20reassess%20its%20doctrine.%20The%20Ukraine%20war%20%26quot%3Bemphasizes%20the%20crucial%20distinction%20between%20innovation%20(combining%20old%20with%20new)%20vs%20adaptation%20(to%20counter%20the%20enemy's%20new%20tactics)%20and%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20both%20(not%20necessarily%20prioritizing%20the%20new)%2C%26quot%3B%20RAND%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%