rmat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuchir%20Balaji%20and%20his%20mom%2C%20Poornima%20Ramarao.%3Cp%3EPoornima%20Ramarao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20moved%20school%20districts%20to%20find%20him%20more%20challenges.%20His%20senior%20year%2C%20he%20was%20the%20US%20champion%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fusaco.org%2Findex.php%3Fpage%3Dopen16results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20programming%20contest%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20high-schoolers%2C%20leading%20to%20him%20getting%20recruited%2C%20at%2017%20years%20old%2C%20by%20Quora%2C%20the%20popular%20online%20knowledge-sharing%20forum.%20His%20mom%20was%20against%20it%2C%20so%20he%20fibbed%20to%20her%20about%20applying.%20But%20he%20had%20to%20fess%20up%20by%20the%20first%20day%20on%20the%20job%20because%20he%20couldn't%20drive%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20give%20him%20a%20ride%20to%20his%20office%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20worried%20about%20how%20he'd%20handle%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%20adults%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20made%20friends%20to%20play%20poker%20with%20and%20enjoyed%20Quora's%20abundant%20cafeteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20lesson%20in%20learning%20to%20trust%20her%20Balaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20understood%2C%20okay%2C%20my%20son%20is%20really%20an%20advanced%20person.%20I%20cannot%20be%20a%20hindrance%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20about%20a%20year%2C%20he%20went%20to%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20and%20soon%20won%20%24100%2C000%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dhs.gov%2Farchive%2Fscience-and-technology%2Fnews%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2Fnews-release-st-announces-winners-15m-prize-competition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSA-sponsored%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20improve%20their%20passenger-screening%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20all%20enough%20to%20be%20re