%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20that%20year%2C%20a%20big%20part%20of%20Balaji's%20role%20was%20gathering%20digital%20data%20%E2%80%94%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20English-speaking%20internet%20%E2%80%94%20for%20GPT-4%2C%20a%20model%20that%20would%20soon%20power%20ChatGPT%2C%20per%20the%20Times%20interview.%20Balaji%20thought%20of%20this%20like%20a%20research%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20other%20people's%20data%20for%20research%20was%20one%20thing%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsuchir.net%2Ffair_use.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20later%20essay.%20Using%20it%20to%20make%20a%20product%20that%20could%20take%20away%20from%20those%20creators'%20revenue%20or%20traffic%20was%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20didn't%20comment%20on%20Balaji's%20concerns%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20In%20court%2C%20it%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20legal%20doctrine%20of%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%26quot%3B%20protects%20how%20its%20models%20ingest%20publicly-available%20internet%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5fab33f-83ef-4399-9c5d-c6d68627336b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BToo%20naive%20and%20too%20innocent%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202023%20and%20early%202024%2C%20Balaji's%20enthusiasm%20for%20OpenAI%20had%20fizzled%20out%20entirely%2C%20and%20he%20began%20to%20criticize%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-chatgpt-worldcoin-helion-future-tech-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20conversations%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20tell%20his%20mom%20when%20he%20was%20working%20on%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20cool%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20more%20and%20more%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20say%20about%20his%20job%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20resigned%20in%20August%2C%20Ramarao%20didn't%20press%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECome%20October%2C%20when%20she%20saw%20his%20bombshell%20interview%20with%20the%20Times%2C%20she%20unleashed%20a%20torrent%20of%20anxiety%20at%20Balaji.%20In%20shining%20a%20spotlight%20on%20what%20he%20thought%20was%20corporate%20wrongdoing%2C%20he%20was%20taking%20it%20all%20on%20his%20shoulders%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20literally%20blasted%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20their%20conversation.%20%26quot%3B'You%20should%20not%20go%20alone.%20Why%20did%20you%20give%20your%20picture%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20give%20your%20name%3F%20Why%20don't%20you%20stay%20anonymous%3F%20What's%20the%20need%20for%20you%20to%20give%20your%20picture%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20go%20as%20a%20group.%20You%20have%20to%20go%20together%20with%20other%20people%20who%20are%20like-minded.%20Then%20he%20said%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20yeah%2C%20yeah.%20I'm%20connecting%20with%20like-minded%20people.%20I'm%20building%20a%20team%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20was%20too%20naive%20and%20too%20innocent%20to%20understand%20this%20dirty%20corporate%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3642132-108f-45d0-8151-47ddb5e60c00%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalaji's%20parents%20are%20calling%20for%20an%20investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Balaji%20left%20OpenAI%20in%20August%2C%20he%20took%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'I'm%20not%20taking%20up%20another%20job.%20Don't%20ask%20me%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Balaji's%20parents'%20vantage%20point%2C%20everything%20seemed%20fine%20with%20the%20young%20coder.%20He%20was%20financially%20stable%2C%20with%20enough%20OpenAI%20stock%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20one%20day%2C%20she%20said.%20He%20had%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20machine%20learning%20non-profit%20in%20the%20medical%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%2C%20a%20Thursday%2C%20Balaji%20celebrated%20his%2026th%20birthday%20with%20friends%20while%20on%20vacation.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20let%20his%20mom%20know%20when%20his%20flight%20home%20took%20off%2C%20and%20spoke%20with%20his%20dad%20on%20the%20phone%20before%20dinner.%20His%20dad%20wished%20him%20a%20happy%20birthday%20and%20said%20he%20was%20sending%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suchir%20Balaji%20with%20friends%20on%20vacation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769b0ba9de00e389eb31289%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuchir%20Balaji%20with%20friends%20on%20vacation.%3Cp%3EPoornima%20Ramarao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ramarao%2C%20the%20medical%20examiner%20said%20that%20Balaji%20died%20that%20evening%2C%20or%20possibly%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20upbeat%20and%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20go%20wrong%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20that%20his%20life%20is%20lost%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%2C%20Ramarao%20didn't%20hear%20from%20her%20son.%20She%20thought%20that%20maybe%20he'd%20lost%20his%20phone%20or%20gone%20for%20a%20hike.%20But%20on%20Monday%2C%20she%20went%20and%20knocked%20on%20his%20door.%20He%20didn't%20answer.%20She%20thought%20about%20filing%20a%20missing%20person%20complaint.%20But%2C%20knowing%20he'd%20have%20to%20go%20in-person%20to%20remove%20it%2C%20she%20hesitated.%20%26quot%3BHe'll%20get%20mad%20at%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20her%20thinking%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20she%20called%20the%20San%20Francisco%20police.%20They%20found%20his%20body%20just%20after%201%20p.m.%20PST%2C%20according%20to%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20department.%20But%20Ramarao%20wasn't%20told%20or%20allowed%20inside%2C%20she%20said.%20As%20officers%20trickled%20in%2C%20she%20pleaded%20with%20them%20to%20check%20if%20his%20laptop%20and%20toothbrush%20were%20missing%2C%20she%20told%20BI%3B%20that%20way%20she'd%20know%20if%20he'd%20traveled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20give%20the%20news%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramaro%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20sitting%20there%20thinking%2C%20'My%20son%20is%20traveling.%20He's%20gone%20somewhere.'%20It's%20such%20a%20pathetic%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202%20p.m.%2C%20they%20told%20her%20to%20go%20home.%20She%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sat%20there%20firmly%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20around%203%3A20%20p.m.%2C%20a%20long%20white%20van%20pulled%20up%20with%20the%20light%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20waiting%20to%20see%20medical%20help%20or%20nurses%20or%20someone%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20van%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20a%20stretcher%20came.%20A%20simple%20stretcher.%20I%20ran%20and%20asked%20the%20person.%20He%20said%2C%20'We%20have%20a%20dead%20body%20in%20that%20apartment.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20a%20medical%20examiner%20and%20police%20asked%20to%20speak%20with%20Ramarao%20one-on-one%20inside%20the%20apartment's%20office.%20They%20said%20that%20Balaji%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20and%20that%20from%20looking%20at%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20he%20was%20alone%2C%20according%20to%20Ramarao.%20There%20was%20no%20initial%20evidence%20of%20foul%20play%2C%20the%20department%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaji's%20parents%20aren't%20convinced.%20They%20arranged%20for%20a%20private%20autopsy%2C%20completed%20in%20early%20December.%20Ramarao%20said%20the%20results%20were%20atypical%2C%20but%20she%20declined%20to%20share%20any%20more%20details.%20BI%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaji's%20parents%20are%20working%20with%20an%20attorney%20to%20press%20the%20SF%20police%20to%20reopen%20the%20case%20and%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bproper%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20they%20and%20members%20of%20their%20community%20are%20trying%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20his%20case%20through%20social%20media%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FChange.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChange.org%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fdemand-a-comprehensive-investigation-into-suchir-balaji-s-death%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Besides%20seeking%20answers%2C%20they%20want%20to%20invoke%20a%20broader%20discussion%20about%20whistleblowers'%20vulnerability%20and%20lack%20of%20protections%2C%20Ramarao%20and%20a%20family%20friend%2C%20who's%20helping%20organize%20a%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1876449042763731%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevent%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Balaji%20on%20December%2027%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20question%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramarao%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20look%20like%20a%20normal%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20shared%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20Ramarao's%20concerns%20and%20memory%20of%20November%2026%20with%20spokespeople%20for%20the%20SF%20police%20and%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Examiner.%20These%20officials%20did%20not%20respond%20or%20offer%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamarao%20emphasized%20to%20BI%20that%20the%20family%20isn't%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suchir%20Balaji%20with%20his%20parents.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769b306e3e473ef263ad25e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuchir%20Balaji%20with%20his%20parents.%3Cp%3EPoornima%20Ramarao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281868347-ac0a-4751-af16-bc49d4c4767a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Yes%2C%20mom'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERamarao%20said%20she%20shared%20a%20close%20bond%20with%20her%20son.%20He%20didn't%20eat%20enough%20fruit%2C%20so%20every%20time%20she%20visited%2C%20she'd%20arrange%20shipments%20to%20his%20apartment%20from%20Costco.%20He%20tended%20to%20skip%20breakfast%2C%20so%20she'd%20bring%20granola%20bars%20and%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaji%20rarely%20expressed%20his%20emotions%20and%20always%20paid%20for%20everything.%20But%20on%20November%207%2C%20during%20their%20last%20meal%20together%2C%20something%20made%20Ramarao%20try%20extra%20hard%20to%20pay%2C%20give%20him%20a%20ride%20home%2C%20and%20seek%20reassurance.%20He%20still%20paid%20for%20the%20meal%20and%20called%20an%20Uber.%20But%20he%20did%20offer%20his%20mom%20two%20words%20of%20encouragement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20him%2C%20'Suchir%20this%20is%20the%20hardship.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20raised%20you%2C%20and%20if%20you%20were%20to%20choose%20parents%20now%2C%20would%20you%20choose%20me%20as%20mom%3F'%20He%20didn't%20think%20for%20a%20second%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3B'Yes%2C%20mom.'%20And%20you%20know%20what%3F%20As%20a%20mother%2C%20that%20will%20keep%20me%20going%20as%20long%20as%20I'm%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuchir-balaji-openai-mom-death-concerns-interview-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735207202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769dc88a3e82c7912041c96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuchir-balaji-openai-mom-death-concerns-interview-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20Poornima%20Ramarao%20shared%20her%20thoughts%20on%20why%20the%20young%20engineer%20soured%20on%20OpenAI%20after%20the%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bdodge%40businessinsider.com%20(Blake%20Dodge)%