story%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20where%20distinguished%20engineers%20are%20expected%20to%20spend%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20their%20time%20on%20enterprise-level%20problems%2C%20not%20unit-specific%20problems%2C%20Pizzi%20said.%20That%20additional%20responsibility%2C%20which%20doesn't%20necessarily%20come%20with%20a%20raise%20or%20promotion%2C%20is%20actually%20a%20plus%20for%20many%20engineers%20in%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20help%20to%20make%20some%20firm-wide%20decisions%20in%20technology%20and%20make%20sure%20we%20are%20moving%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ken%20Zhang%2C%20one%20of%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20newest%20DEs%20and%20one%20of%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20bank's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-morgan-stanley-ai-leader-vets-new-solutions-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20tool%2C%20AskResearch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFang%20Song%2C%20another%20newly%20minted%20Morgan%20Stanley%20DE%20and%20executive%20director%20in%20the%20enterprise%20computing%20group%2C%20referred%20to%20her%20peers%20as%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20influencers%26quot%3B%20who%20make%20widely%20impacting%20decisions%20on%20reusable%20technology%20blueprints%20that%20are%20used%20across%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5ce40b4-1224-484e-970f-e31f327a1235%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20a%20distinguished%20engineer%20or%20technical%20fellow%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Morgan%20Stanley%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20distinguished%20engineers%20and%20technical%20fellows%20cannot%20apply%20for%20the%20designation.%20They%20must%20be%20nominated%20by%20senior%20management%20or%20existing%20TFs%20and%20DEs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20engineering%20excellence%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20being%20a%20DE%20and%20TF%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20candidates%20are%20judged%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20Pizzi%20said%20contributing%20to%20the%20firm's%20technical%20reputation%20externally%20is%20important%2C%20whether%20it%20involves%20writing%20technical%20books%20and%20white%20papers%20or%20holding%20patents.%20The%20bank's%20DEs%20hold%20one%20third%20of%20the%20patents%20the%20bank%20has%20generated%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20judges%20candidates%20on%20how%20they%20nurture%20the%20broader%20technology%20population.%20Stratan%20said%20she%20remembers%20and%20keeps%20in%20touch%20with%20her%20mentors%2C%20who%20taught%20her%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20be%20a%20senior%20engineer%20and%20how%20to%20think%20through%20complex%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20important%20piece%20is%20mentoring%20and%20coaching%2C%26quot%3B%20Stratan%20said.%20%26quot%3BBasically%20the%20tech%20fellows%20are%20coaching%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20tech%20talent%20at%20the%20firm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-rise-wall-street-tech-fellows-distinguished-engineers-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735207202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676990ace3e473ef263ac78a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-rise-wall-street-tech-fellows-distinguished-engineers-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20technologists%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20Here's%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20what%20they%20do%20and%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20become%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-rise-wall-street-tech-fellows-distinguished-engineers-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20year%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20private%20jet%20travels%20reveals%20his%20deepening