%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5yg57wrgl7o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5yg57wrgl7o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Escapes%20Ban%20But%20Fined%20Over%20Konstas%20Clash%20In%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20former%20India%20captain%2C%20has%20been%20fined%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20match%20fee%20in%20the%20India%20vs%20Australia%204th%20Test%20in%20Melbourne%20after%20a%20shoulder%20barge%20incident%20with%20debutant%20Sam%20Konstas%20on%20Thursday%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0The%20incident%20happened%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%2010th%20over%20of%20the%20Australian%20innings%20when%20the%20players%20were%20crossing%20over.%20Kohli%20and%20Konstas%20bumped%20shoulders%20while%20moving%20across%20the%20pitch.%20Both%20players%20quickly%20turned%20around%20to%20glance%20at%20each%20other%20and%20engage%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20of%20words%20with%20Konstas'%20teammate%20Usman%20Khawaja%20stepping%20in%20to%20separate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20on-field%20umpires%20also%20had%20a%20word%20with%20the%20two.%20%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20has%20been%20slapped%20with%20a%20Level%201%20offence.%20He%20has%20been%20fined%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20match%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20NDTV.%20After%20incident%2C%20many%20former%20players%20predicted%20that%20Kohli%20may%20face%20suspension%20but%20that%20has%20not%20happened%20as%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20a%20Level%201%20offence.%C2%A0Level%202%20offences%20carry%20a%20penalty%20of%20three%20to%20four%20demerit%20points.%20Four%20demerit%20points%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20suspension%20of%20one%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20states%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20form%20of%20inappropriate%20physical%20contact%20is%20prohibited%20in%20cricket.%20Without%20limitation%2C%20players%20will%20breach%20this%20regulation%20if%20they%20deliberately%2C%20recklessly%20and%2For%20negligently%20walk%20or%20run%20into%20or%20shoulder%20another%20player%20or%20umpire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKohli%20and%20Konstas%20come%20together%20and%20make%20contact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAUSvIND%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AUSvIND%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fadb09clEqd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fadb09clEqd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%207Cricket%20(%407Cricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7Cricket%2Fstatus%2F1872075722249912813%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20Stumps%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%2C%20Konstas%20said%20Kohli%20bumped%20into%20him%20and%20it%20wasn't%20deliberate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20accidentally%20bumped%20into%20me%2C%20that's%20cricket%20and%20can%20happen%20with%20tension%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20teenager.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20emotions%20got%20to%20both%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Konstas%20had%20told%20'Channel%207'%20during%20the%20second%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20quite%20realise%2C%20I%20was%20doing%20my%20gloves%2C%20then%20a%20little%20shoulder%20charge%2C%20but%20it%20happens%20in%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKonstas%2C%20who%20was%20batting%20on%2027%20at%20the%20time%2C%20went%20on%20to%20hit%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20for%20two%20boundaries%20and%20a%20six%20in%20the%20next%20over.%20The%20teenager%20scored%20a%20stunning%20fifty%20on%20debut%20before%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20trapped%20him%20leg%20before%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MessageBody%5C%22%3EKonstas%20might%20have%20dismissed