0worry%20about%20overconsumption%20and%20our%20planet%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20effects%20on%20my%20own%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-marketplace-this-feature-annoys-sellers-is-this-still-available-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20love%20Facebook%20Marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20scratches%20the%20itch%20for%20mindless%20consumption%20in%20a%20more%20sustainable%20way.%20I'm%20simply%20%3Cem%3Evirtuous%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20my%20place%20in%20Heaven%20secured!%20%E2%80%94%20for%20buying%20a%20used%208-by-10%20rug%20in%20good%20condition%20for%20%2475%20instead%20of%20a%20brand-new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20probably%20spend%20more%20time%20browsing%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20than%20I%20spend%20on%20lots%20of%20other%20interesting%20and%20popular%20things.%20My%20iPhone's%20screen%20time%20tells%20me%20that%20I%20spent%20more%20time%20on%20the%20Facebook%20app%20last%20week%20than%20TikTok%2C%20Slack%2C%20or%20Bluesky.%20And%20you'll%20have%20to%20just%20believe%20me%20when%20I%20tell%20you%20that%20I%20spent%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20time%20on%20those%20other%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20have%20a%20very%20specific%20and%20very%20real%20gripe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20Marketplace%20shows%20me%20listings%20for%20items%20located%20across%20a%20body%20of%20water%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20items%20are%20within%20my%20specified%20distance%20radius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20explain%3A%20For%20local%20listings%2C%20you%20can%20select%20a%20distance%20range%20of%20a%20set%20number%20of%20miles%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20few%2C%20or%20even%20farther%2C%20say%2050%20miles.%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20will%20then%20create%20a%20perfect%20circle%20of%20that%20search%20radius%2C%20giving%20you%20as-the-crow-flies%20distance%20in%20every%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20reality%2C%2010%20miles%20to%20the%20east%20isn't%20always%20the%20same%20as%2010%20miles%20to%20the%20west.%20%3Cem%3EEspecially%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20cases%20where%20a%20river%20or%20body%20of%20water%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22map%20of%20brooklyn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67635040b1d5f0276b36d31e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFour%20miles%20around%20downtown%20Brooklyn%20will%20show%20you%20New%20Jersey%20results.%3Cp%3Escreenshot%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%20%2F%20Facebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20I'm%20in%20downtown%20Brooklyn.%20If%20I%20search%20a%204-mile%20radius%2C%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20will%20show%20me%20items%20for%20sale%20deeper%20into%20Brooklyn%2C%20easily%20accessible%20by%20car%20or%20subway%2C%20and%20it%20will%20also%20show%20me%20results%20in%20lower%20Manhattan%20(more%20annoying%20to%20drive%20to)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20worst%20of%20all%2C%20it%20will%20also%20give%20some%20results%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20by%20no%20means%20a%20knock%20on%20the%20great%20Garden%20State.%20In%20fact%2C%20I've%20often%20observed%20in%20my%20Marketplace%20searching%20that%20New%20Jersey%20has%20some%20of%20the%20most%20desirable%20furniture%20and%20other%20items.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20pain%20to%20get%20from%20Brooklyn%20to%20New%20Jersey%20just%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20used%20end%20table%E2%80%94%20the%20tolls%20alone%20make%20it%20not%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20searching%20around%20suburban%20Connecticut%2C%20where%20things%20are%20more%20spread%20out%2C%20and%2020%20miles%20of%20driving%20isn't%20unreasonable.%20However%2C%20this%20creates%20a%20big%20enough%20search%20radius%20that%20it%20extends%20across%20the%20Long%20Island%20Sound%2C%20into%20the%20northern%20tips%20of%20Long%20Island.%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20idea%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20to%20drive%20from%20Bridgeport%2C%20Connecticut%20to%20Huntington%20Station%2C%20New%20York%3F%20Long%20enough%20to%3Cem%3E%20drop%20dead%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that's%20how%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20just%20an%20East%20Coast%20problem%2C%20either.%20In%20fact%2C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20employees%2C%20this%20should%20hit%20close%20to%20home.%20Menlo%20Park%2C%20California%20%E2%80%94%20where%20Meta%20is%20based%20%E2%80%94%20is%20located%20along%20a%20body%20of%20water.%20That%20makes%20it%20quite%20annoying%20to%20get%20to%20the%20land%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20bay%2C%20either%20by%20public%20transportation%20or%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22map%20of%20melo%20park%2C%20ca%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676355f5b1d5f0276b36d38e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta's%20HQ%20in%20Menlo%20Park%20means%20going%20across%20the%20bay%20is%20annoying.%3Cp%3Escreenshot%20%2F%20Facebook%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20proposed%20solution%20here%3A%20One%20option%20could%20be%20that%20instead%20of%20making%20a%20perfect%20circle%20of%20a%20search%20radius%2C%20you%20could%20draw%20your%20own%20search%20shape%20with%20your%20finger.%20Zillow%20has%20a%20version%20of%20this%20that%20it%20uses%20for%20its%20home%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20preference%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20to%20factor%20in%20driving%20distance%20or%20public%20transit%20access.%20It%20would%20be%20great%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BShow%20me%20all%20the%20coffee%20tables%20within%2030%20minutes%20driving%20distance%2C%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20a%20perfect%20circle%20on%20a%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20a%20representative%20for%20Meta%20if%20they%20viewed%20the%20water%20issue%20as%20a%20problem%2C%20they%20seemed%20slightly%20puzzled%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20seeing%20things%20that%20were%20actually%20errors%20%E2%80%94%20results%20outside%20the%20specified%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Meta%20doesn't%20really%20directly%20profit%20from%20these%20in-person%20Marketplace%20transactions%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you%20show%20up%20at%20someone's%20home%20and%20hand%20them%20cash%20for%20their%20stuff.%20(Meta%20does%20take%20a%20cut%20if%20the%20monetary%20transaction%20is%20completed%20on%20Facebook%2C%20typically%20for%20shipped%20items.)%20It%20may%20not%20be%20a%20big%20profit%20center%20for%20Meta%2C%20but%20it%20definitely%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-marketplace-key-to-meta-getting-gen-z-younger-users-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarketplace%20is%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20Facebook's%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy%20for%20young%20people.%20Despite%20its%20sometimes%20fuddy-duddy%20reputation%2C%20Facebook%20is%20actually%C2%A0%3Cem%3Egrowing%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0its%20Gen%20Z%20user%20base.%20So%2C%20improving%20Marketplace%20is%20important%20to%20Facebook's%20overall%20health.%20Many%20young%20people%20tend%20to%20live%20in%20urban%20areas%20near%20bodies%20of%20water%20(rivers%2C%20bays%2C%20oceans).%20No%20one%20wants%20to%20have%20to%20drive%20over%20a%20bridge%20to%20buy%20a%20couch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20plea%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-spars-mma-fighters-floating-barge-video-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekickboxing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20focus%20in%20on%20this%20important%20issue.%20End%20the%20Marketplace%20search%20that%20goes%20across%20water%20boundaries!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2