efruit%20%E2%80%94%20called%20out%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20messed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20glaze%20should%20taste%20amazing.%20But%20it%20didn't.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20bowl%20of%20the%20ginger%2C%20miso%2C%20grapefruit%20and%20honey%20glaze%20for%20New%20York%20Times%20Cooking's%20Sticky%20Miso%20Salmon%20Bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676527eb5cddac6581d72d7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarmalade%2C%20basically.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe%20called%20for%20two%20teaspoons%20of%20fresh%20grapefruit%20zest.%20But%20as%20I%20tasted%20the%20glaze%20it%20was%20off-the-charts%20bitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20restarted%20with%20half%20as%20much%20zest%20and%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20marmalade-like%20substance%20to%20coat%20the%20salmon%2C%20hoping%20that%20the%20broiling%20process%20would%20mellow%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'd%20cook%20the%20dish%20again%2C%20but%20would%20be%20much%20more%20careful.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20York%20Times%20Cooking's%20Sticky%20Miso%20Salmon%20bowl%20on%20a%20dish%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0served%20with%20buttered%20rice%20with%20diced%20scallions%2C%20sushi%20nori%2C%20and%20sliced%20avocado.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67652a4d5cddac6581d72d93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFresh%20avocado%20worked%20perfectly%20with%20the%20fatty%20salmon%20and%20buttery%20rice.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20that%20the%20grapefruit%20%E2%80%94%20citrusy%2C%20aromatic%2C%20and%20a%20little%20bitter%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20stand-out%20flavor%20twist%20for%20this%20recipe.