C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20able%20to%20make%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcooking.nytimes.com%2Frecipes%2F1025014-cheesy-green-chile-bean-bake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECheesy%20Green%20Chile%20Bean%20Bake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20fifth%20on%20the%20list%2C%20due%20to%20not%20being%20able%20to%20get%20my%20hands%20on%20pinto%20beans%2C%20so%20I%20turned%20to%20the%20sixth%20choice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcooking.nytimes.com%2Frecipes%2F1025047-peanut-butter-noodles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeanut%20Butter%20Noodles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20section%20on%20this%20recipe%20is%20a%20massive%20love-in%20%E2%80%94%20people%20are%20wild%20for%20this%20extremely%20simple%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20eat%20this%20alone%2C%20naked%2C%20in%20a%20closet.%20It's%20that%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20commenter%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20curious%20to%20see%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20just%205%20simple%20ingredients.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223630%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ingredients%20for%20New%20York%20Times%20Cooking's%20Peanut%20Butter%20Noodles%20in%20a%20pan%2C%20comprising%20cooked%20spaghetti%2C%20grated%20parmesan%2C%20a%20spoonful%20of%20soy%20sauce%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20butter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67654bb81cee543535a8743d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20dubious%20at%20this%20stage.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dish%20involves%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20ingredients%3A%20noodles%2C%20butter%2C%20soy%20sauce%2C%20Parmesan%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20peanut%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20about%20the%20recipe%20seems%20designed%20to%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20possible%3A%20You're%20encouraged%20to%20use%20the%20cheapest%20peanut%20butter%20you%20can%20find%2C%20and%20the%20noodles%20are%20from%20packet%20ramen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20spaghetti%2C%20so%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20science%2C%20I%20resolved%20to%20try%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20spaghetti%20was%20a%20disaster%2C%20but%20the%20ramen%20worked%20well.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20composite%20image%20showing%20forkfuls%20of%20New%20York%20Times%20Cooking's%20Peanut%20Butter%20noodles.%20Left%2C%20with%20spaghetti%2C%20and%20right%2C%20with%20ramen%20noodles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765506c5cddac6581d72f66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20perplexed%20by%20this%20dish.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dish%20is%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20cooking%20your%20spaghetti%2Framen%2C%20then%20mixing%20some%20of%20the%20cooking%20water%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ingredients%20to%20make%20a%20glossy%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20tasted%20the%20spaghetti%20version%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20wasn't%20for%20me%3A%20they%20were%20just%20too%20thick%20and%20heavy%20with%20the%20cloying%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20texture%20with%20the%20springier%20noodles%2C%20however%2C%20had%20just%20the%20right%20chew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20making%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe%20is%20clearly%20designed%20to%20be%20an%20umami-fest%20that%20you%20can%20blearily%20throw%20together%20after%20a%20night%20out.%20But%20it%20was%20just%20too%20bland%20and%20salty%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20this%20was%20a%20great%20adventure%20for%20me%20and%20my%20assistant.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223644%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20writer's%20kitchen%20counter%20midway%20through%20preparing%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20cooking%20recipe%2C%20with%20a%20smiling%20cat%20sitting%20behind%20an