2F676af119e3e473ef263b0628%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Ftax-exempt-interest-income%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Discover%20how%20to%20earn%20tax-free%20interest%20income%20through%20investments.%20Understand%20the%20rules%20and%20benefits%20of%20tax-exempt%20interest%20and%20find%20suitable%20options%20for%20you.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tanza%20Loudenback%2CLisa%20Niser%2C%20EA)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Ftax-exempt-interest-income%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20extremely%20rare%20for%20prisoners%20to%20win%20lawsuits%20on%20Eighth%20Amendment%20claims.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20of%20their%20house%20holding%20a%20picture%20of%20their%20son.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675346fc8fb3f94e5073f5dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristy%20and%20Darren%20Smith%20with%20a%20portrait%20of%20their%20late%20son%2C%20Joshua%20England%2C%20in%20front%20of%20their%20home%20in%20Fairview%2C%20Oklahoma.%20He%20died%20of%20a%20ruptured%20appendix%20while%20serving%20a%20one-year%20sentence%20at%20an%20Oklahoma%20prison%20called%20Joseph%20Harp.%3Cp%3ENick%20Oxford%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20span%20of%20days%2C%20Joshua%20England's%20pleas%20for%20help%20became%20more%20desperate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20puking%20all%20night%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20puking%20what%20looks%20like%20blood%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20to%20his%20medical%20providers%20on%20May%2022%2C%202018.%20%26quot%3BMy%20stomach%20hurts%20so%2C%20so%20bad.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20medical%20clinic%20that%20day%20he%20clutched%20his%20abdomen%20and%20described%20his%20pain%20as%20sharp%20and%20intense%20%E2%80%94%20an%208%20out%20of%2010.%20But%20he%20was%20seen%20by%20a%20lesser-trained%20licensed%20practical%20nurse%2C%20who%20didn't%20give%20him%20a%20complete%20abdominal%20exam%20or%20send%20him%20for%20any%20lab%20work.%20Instead%20he%20was%20given%20Pepto-Bismol%20and%20told%20to%20drink%20water%20and%20eat%20fibrous%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pepto-Bismol%20didn't%20help.%20The%20next%20day%20England%20wrote%20that%20his%20pain%20was%20so%20bad%20he%20could%20barely%20breathe.%20He%20couldn't%20eat%20or%20sleep.%20He%20again%20went%20to%20the%20clinic%2C%20where%20he%20said%20he'd%20had%20bloody%20stool%20and%20his%20pain%20was%20now%20a%2010%20out%20of%2010.%20The%20physician%20assistant%20found%20that%20his%20pulse%20was%20racing%20but%20didn't%20conduct%20an%20abdominal%20exam.%20Instead%2C%20he%20chalked%20up%20England's%20symptoms%20to%20constipation%20and%20prescribed%20a%20laxative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%20someone%20with%20England's%20symptoms%20might%20seek%20out%20a%20new%20clinic%2C%20to%20get%20a%20more%20thorough%20workup%2C%20or%20even%20head%20straight%20to%20an%20ER.%20But%20Joshua%20England%20didn't%20have%20that%20option.%20He%20was%20inmate%20No.%20775261%20at%20Joseph%20Harp%20Correctional%20Center%2C%20a%20medium-security%20facility%20in%20central%20Oklahoma.%20He'd%20been%20sentenced%20to%20343%20days%20in%20prison%20after%20he%20and%20some%20buddies%20set%20some%20hay%20bales%20on%20fire%20one%20drunken%20night.%20This%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20events%20of%20those%20days%20in%20May%202018%20is%20based%20on%20prison%20and%20medical%20records%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.readfrontier.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Frontier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20newsroom%20in%20Oklahoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221596%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Oklahoma%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20%26quot%3Brequest%20for%20health%20services%26quot%3B%20form%2C%20filled%20in%20by%20hand%2C%20reads%20in%20part%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20puking%20all%20night.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675896cd52dd0818d1a64b92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20May%202018%2C%20England%20submitted%20a%20handwritten%20request%20for%20health%20services%20that%20described%20excruciating%20stomach%20pain.%3Cp%3EOklahoma%20Department%20of%20Corrections%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20after%20he%20first%20requested%20help%2C%20England%20submitted%20his%20fourth%20sick%20call%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one-page%20form%20that%20prisoners%20at%20Joseph%20Harp%20used%20to%20request%20medical%20attention.%20He%20again%20wrote%20down%20how%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20breathe%20or%20even%20lie%20down.%20This%20time%20the%20licensed%20practical%20nurse%20who%20saw%20him%20consulted%20with%20the%20prison's%20supervising%20physician%2C%20Robert%20Balogh.%20Balogh%20prescribed%20ibuprofen%20over%20the%20phone.%20He%2C%20and%20the%20physician%20assistant%20who%20saw%20England%20earlier%2C%20each%20had%20marks%20on%20their%20records%3A%20Balogh%20had%20been%20fined%20and%20put%20on%20probation%20for%20a%20time%20by%20the%20Oklahoma%20narcotics%20bureau%2C%20and%20the%20license%20of%20the%20PA%20had%20once%20been%20revoked%20for%20prescription%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20medical%20professionals%20downplayed%20England's%20symptoms%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20deteriorate.%20He%20couldn't%20work%20or%20eat%20or%20shower%3B%20instead%20he%20remained%20in%20his%20cell%2C%20curled%20up%20on%20the%20floor%20in%20tears.%20Other%20prisoners%20reported%20that%20he%20had%20lost%20weight%2C%20his%20skin%20color%20had%20changed%2C%20and%20he%20no%20longer%20seemed%20fully%20cognizant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2029%2C%202018%2C%20a%20corrections%20officer%20discovered%20England%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25262688-joshua-england-incident-report%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslumped%20over%20on%20the%20floor%20next%20to%20his%20cell%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Choctaw%20Nation%20kid%20who%20loved%20fishing%20and%20cattle%20ranching%20had%20died%2C%20just%20weeks%20after%20turning%2021.%20Autopsy%20records%20show%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20a%20ruptured%20appendix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAppendicitis%20is%20easily%20treated%20with%20minimally%20invasive%20outpatient%20surgery.%20Even%20treating%20a%20ruptured%20appendix%20is%20considered%20routine%20as%20long%20as%20the%20patient%20is%20immediately%20hospitalized.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20PA%20was%20notified%20of%20his%20declining%20condition%20the%20morning%20of%20his%20death%3B%20he%20later%20told%20investigators%20he%20didn't%20believe%20England's%20condition%20had%20been%20life-threatening.%20A%20licensed%20practical%20nurse%20who%20saw%20England%20a%20few%20days%20earlier%20said%20she%20suspected%20he%20was%20in%20withdrawal%20and%20seeking%20painkillers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christy%20Smith%20and%20husband%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wall%20covered%20in%20crosses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675350378fb3f94e5073fb3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Smiths%20at%20home%20in%20Fairview.%20On%20May%2029%2C%202018%2C%20a%20corrections%20officer%20discovered%20their%20son%20slumped%20over%20on%20the%20floor%20next%20to%20his%20cell.%20He%20had%20been%20complaining%20of%20acute%20pain%20for%20a%20week.%3Cp%3ENick%20Oxford%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20after%20England's%20death%2C%20the%20Oklahoma%20legislature%20approved%20a%20%241.05%20million%20settlement%20with%20h