%20once%20called%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-suspend-ai-chip-production-china-us-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company's%3C%2Fa%3E%20chip%20plants%20if%20China%20takes%20over%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20scenario%20in%20which%20Taiwan%20falls%20to%20the%20PRC%20and%20Taiwanese%20can%20expect%20TSMC%20and%20its%20central%20role%20to%20persist%2C%26quot%3B%20Colby%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20Pentagon%20official%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FElbridgeColby%2Fstatus%2F1660266710379683840%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20thread%20in%20May%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20China%20attacks%20Taiwan%2C%20Taiwan%20itself%20and%20US%20should%20not%20allow%20TSMC%20to%20fall%20intact%20into%20PRC%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Colby%20wrote%20in%20the%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%2C%20Colby%20wrote%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20US'%20semiconductor%20sanctions%20against%20China%20in%20the%20event%20that%20Taiwan%20surrenders.%20The%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20can't%20afford%20to%20allow%20China%20to%20%26quot%3Bhave%20such%20dominance%20over%20global%20semiconductors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20announced%20Colby's%20nomination%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113698633761724468%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20respected%20advocate%20for%20our%20America%20First%20foreign%20and%20defense%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColby%2C%20a%20Harvard%20and%20Yale%20Law%20graduate%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration.%20He%20served%20as%20Trump's%20deputy%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20defense%20for%20strategy%20and%20force%20development%20from%202017%20to%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColby%20made%20a%20similar%20point%20about%20TSMC%20in%20another%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FElbridgeColby%2Fstatus%2F1761514916224139737%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisabling%20or%20destroying%20TSMC%20is%20table%20stakes%20if%20China%20is%20taking%20over%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20Colby%20wrote%20on%20February%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20we%20be%20so%20insane%20as%20to%20allow%20the%20world's%20key%20semiconductor%20company%20fall%20untouched%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20an%20aggressive%20PRC%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Trump%20and%20Colby%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20TSMC%20also%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20contract%20chipmaker.%20It%20counts%20US%20tech%20giants%20like%20Apple%20and%20Nvidia%20as%20major%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20core%20base%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20is%20also%20home%20to%20smaller%20chip%20producers%20like%20MediaTek%20and%20ASE%2C%20making%20the%20island%20a%20critical%20node%20in%20the%20global%20semiconductor%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semiconductors.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FBCG-x-SIA-Strengthening-the-Global-Semiconductor-Value-Chain-April-2021_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESemiconductor%20Industry%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2092%25%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20advanced%20microchips%20are%20produced%20in%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Gina%20Raimondo%20told%20lawmakers%20at%20a%20House%20hearing%20that%20a%20Chinese%20seizure%20of%20TSMC%20during%20a%20Taiwan%20invasion%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-official-says-chinese-seizure-tsmc-taiwan-would-be-absolutely-devastating-2024-05-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20be%20absolutely%20devastating%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20The%20US%20is%20obliged%20by%20law%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F96th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F2479%2Fall-info%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotect%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20the%20island%20with%20military%20means%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20US%20has%20strived%20to%20diversify%20its%20chip%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20Biden%20signed%20the%20%2452%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchips-act-funding-biden-administration-trump-tariffs-repeal-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECHIPS%20for%20America%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20manufacturing%20incentives%20for%20chip%20production%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20drew%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-tariffs-chips-could-create-more-american-jobs-increase-prices-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticism%20from%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fepisode%2F0e9ynAH6hmZIIeOx0SaGQu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Joe%20Rogan%20in%20October%20that%20tariffs%2C%20not%20subsidies%2C%20would%20have%20been%20more%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20have%20done%20it%20with%20tariffs.%20You%20tariff%20it%20so%20high%20that%20they%20will%20come%20and%20build%20their%20chip%20companies%20for%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-us-export-controls-china-tech-ai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20raft%20of%20export%20controls%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20China's%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%2C%20which%20target%20140%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20mark%20the%20third%20time%20the%20administration%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20China's%20chipmaking%20industry%20since%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20companies%20like%20Huawei%2C%20Naura%20Technology%20Group%2C%20and%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20International%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-defense-pick-us-destroy-tsmc-if-china-takes-taiwan-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735203607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676ce10da3e82c7912046127%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-defense-pick-us-destroy-tsmc-if-china-takes-taiwan-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDisabling%20or%20destroying%20TSMC%20is%20table%20stakes%20if%20China%20is%20taking%20over%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20senior%20Pentagon%20official%20Elbridge%20Colby%20said%20in%20February.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-defense-pick-us-destroy-tsmc-if-china-takes-taiwan-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Attempt%20To%20Kill%20Me'%3A%20BJP%20MLA%20Claims%20'Egg%20Attack'%20On%20Him%20In%20Bengaluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20egg%20attack%20on%20BJP%20MLA%20N.%20Munirathna%20Naidu%20in%20Bengaluru.%20In%20the%20complaint%2C%20MLA%20Munirathna%20said%20the%20act%20was%20part%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20attack%20and%20murder%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20taken%20three%20persons%20into%20custody%20from%20the%20spot%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.