E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20made%20lewd%2C%20sexual%20comments%2C%20and%20showed%20Lively%20nude%20images%20of%20other%20women%2C%20including%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20walked%20into%20Blake's%20trailer%20while%20she%20was%20breastfeeding.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20and%20Jamey%20Heath%20discussed%20pornography%20and%20Baldoni's%20previous%20addiction.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20claimed%20he%20could%20communicate%20with%20Lively's%20recently%20dead%20father.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lively%20complained%20about%20the%20men%20on%20the%20set%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20violating%20personal%20boundaries%20and%20made%20sexual%20and%20other%20inappropriate%20comments%20to%20her%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20studio%20agreed%20to%20have%20on%20board%20an%20intimacy%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20men%2C%20Baldoni%20and%20CEO%20Heath%2C%20it%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20long%20and%20orchestrated%20smear%20campaign%20against%20the%20actress%2C%20claims%20Lively's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaldoni%20allegedly%20hired%20the%20crisis%20management%20agency%20TAG%20to%2C%20well%2C%20manage%20the%20crisis%20with%20Baldoni%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20it.%20Melissa%20Nathan%2C%20Baldoni's%20crisis%20manager%2C%20has%20among%20her%20former%20clients%20Drake%2C%20Travis%20Scott%20and%20Johnny%20Depp.%20It%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20all%20rosy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20promotions%20for%20the%20film%2C%20hawk-eyed%20Internet%20sleuths%20spotted%20something%20wrong.%20Baldoni%20was%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20Blake%20Lively%20was%20at%20the%20promotions%20without%20Baldoni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20New%20York%20premiere%20of%20%3Cem%3EIt%20Ends%20With%20Us%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Blake%20was%20accompanied%20by%20her%20husband%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20and%20co-star%20Brandon%20Sklenar.%C2%A0Baldoni%20was%20missing%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20take%20a%20Sherlock%20Holmes%20to%20sniff%20