2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20startup's%20SMRs%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fvideos%2Fnewcleo-is-building-nuclear-reactor-waste-fuel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20plutonium%20and%20uranium%20radioactive%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20fuel%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukinventory.nda.gov.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F01%2FFact-sheet-spent-fuel-reprocessing.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparating%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20two%20elements%20from%20the%20unwanted%20fission%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20using%20and%20reducing%20what%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20liability%20and%20a%20strong%20concern%20for%20all%20the%20governments%20who%20have%20so%20many%20deposits%20of%20nuclear%20waste%2C%26quot%3B%20Elisabeth%20Rizzotti%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20Newcleo%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20also%20promised%20to%20reduce%20them.%20And%20this%20is%20a%20story%20that%20really%20excites%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech's%20push%20into%20nuclear%20has%20galvanized%20the%20startup's%20efforts.%20Tech%20giants%20such%20as%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-openai-big-tech-investment-nuclear-ai-race-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epivoting%20to%20nuclear%20energy%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20power%20data%20centers%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20power%20AI%20applications.%20In%20September%2C%20Microsoft%20announced%20a%20deal%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-mile-island-nuclear-plant-reopens-power-microsoft-ai-push-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestart%20Three%20Mile%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nuclear%20plant%20infamous%20for%20housing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20nuclear%20accidents%20in%20US%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c747cd35-1662-447d-83c2-720381b21f45%5C%22%3ELocalized%20nuclear%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENewcleo%20is%20one%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20companies%20developing%20SMRs.%20Competitors%20include%20NuScale%2C%20X-Energy%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolls-royce-micro-nuclear-power-space-missions-data-centers-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERolls-Royce%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20appeal%20of%20SMRs%20is%20that%20they%20can%20be%20readily%20transported%20to%20industrial%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20our%20most%20relevant%20business%20models%20is%20supporting%20the%20industrial%20sector%2C%20in%20providing%20them%20energy%20locally%2C%26quot%3B%20Rizzotti%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20small%20models%20are%20easily%20transportable%20because%20they're%20flexible%2C%20and%20you%20can%20build%20them%20in%20the%20factory%2C%20so%20it's%20very%20feasible%20%E2%80%94%20so%20there%20is%20strong%20interest%20from%20the%20AI%20sector%2C%20but%20also%20wider%20commercial%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20Newcleo%20has%20been%20approached%20by%20other%20industrial%20sectors%2C%20such%20as%20ceramic%20metal%20producers%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20those%20in%20the%20AI%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecuring%20industrial%20partnerships%20is%20key%20to%20Newcleo's%20growth%20strategy%20and%20fundraising%20efforts.%20The%20startup%20aims%20to%20develop%20its%20first%20prototype%20by%202026%20and%20operate%20its%20first%20reactor%20by%202031.%20Right%20now%2C%20Newcleo%20is%20lossmaking%2C%20but%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20hit%20around%20%2455%20million%20in%20revenue%20through%20its%20three%20subsidiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222034%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Newcleo%20render%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676190fa6c531c315b88bd9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendered%20image%20of%20Newcleo's%20reactor%20design.%3Cp%3ENewcleo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22847db533-7be0-4923-911e-69e44f7c60fd%5C%22%3EGrowth%20ambitions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Newcleo%20moved%20its%20headquarters%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Paris%2C%20which%20Rizzotti%20said%20was%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20the%20French%20government%20and%20support%20its%20licensing%20applications.%20The%20move%20helped%20Newcleo%20get%20selected%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20European%20Industrial%20Alliance%20on%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20accelerate%20the%20deployment%20of%20SMRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20public%20and%20private%20sector%20interest%2C%20nuclear%20energy%20is%20still%20seen%20by%20some%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-european-nuclear-startups-to-watch-according-to-vcs-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisky%20enterprise%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20safety%20concerns%20and%20the%20hefty%20upfront%20cost%20of%20building%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERizzotti%20acknowledged%20that%20Newcleo's%20investors%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20risk%20appetite%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20says%20Newcleo's%20place%20in%20the%20circular%20economy%20makes%20it%20an%20attractive%20investment%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Newcleo%20announced%20a%20bold%20ambition%20to%20raise%20%E2%82%AC1%20billion%2C%20about%20%241.04%20billion.%20It's%20now%20over%20halfway%20to%20meeting%20that%20target%2C%20having%20raised%20over%20%24560%20million%20in%20funding%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Pi%20Campus%2C%20Tosto%20Group%2C%20and%20Viaro%20Energy%20since%20its%20launch%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20future%20capital-raising%20strategy%20will%20also%20partially%20depend%20on%20public%20funds.%20%26quot%3BAt%20a%20European%20level%2C%20energy%20independence%20is%20something%20that%20we%20need%20to%20consider%2C%26quot%3B%20Rizzotti%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20important%20to%20have%20a%20partnership%20between%20the%20public%20and%20private%2C%20because%20public%20investment%20will%20reassure%20private%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20also%20sees%20an%20IPO%20as%20a%20viable%20exit%20option%20in%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BSooner%20or%20later%2C%20we%20will%20start%20the%20project%20of%20an%20IPO%2C%20so%20the%20perspective%20of%20being%20public%20allows%20people%20and%20investors%20to%20have%20shares%20of%20a%20company%20that%20is%20recognized%20in%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Rizzotti%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20tangible%20asset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rizzotti%20did%20not%20have%20a%20set%20timeline%20for%20the%20company%20going%20public%2C%20she%20added%20that%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20after%20the%20startup%20achieved%20a%20second%20key%20milestone%20after%20its%20first%20prototype%20in%202026%3A%20pre-authorization%20to%20build%20its%20first%20reactor%20in%20France%20by%20early%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20obtain%20these%20two%20milestones%2C%20in%20our%20opinion%2C%20we%20could%20be%20ready%20to%20go%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20money%20through%20more%20natural%20channels%20like%20private%20equity%20or%20venture%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewcleo-coo-nuclear-startup-europe-small-modular-reactor-ipo-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735201801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67605a6127808b3289cd56ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewcleo-coo-nuclear-startup-europe-small-modular-reactor-ipo-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Newcleo's%20cofounder%20and%20COO%20says%20the%20startup%2C%20which%20is%20Europe's%20only%20nuclear%20unicorn%2C%20will%20IPO%20after%20hitting%20two%20key%20milestones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rkanetkar%40insider.com%20(Riddhi%20Kanetkar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewcleo-coo-nuclear-startup-europe-small-modular-reactor-ipo-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20Protects%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elderly%20From%20Financial%20Uncertainty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAccessing%20healthcare%20often%20becomes%20an%20uphill%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383324%2Fkhyaal-app-senior-citizens-living-ageing-community-virtual%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20for%20senior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20financial%20burden%20of%20treatments%20acting%20as%20a%20significant%20barrier.%20Many%20older%20adults%20find%20themselves%20postponing%20or%20forgoing%20critical%20medical%20care%20primarily%20due%20to%20fear%20and%20also%20due%20to%20skyrocketing%20costs%2C%20which%20can%20jeopardise%20their%20health%20and%20well-being.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20this%20challenge%2C%20the%20Indian%20Government%20introduced%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20on%20September%2012%2C%202024%2C%20a%20welcoming%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20that%20financial%20constraints%20no%20longer%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20healthcare%20for%20senior%20citizens%20aged%2070%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scheme%20provides%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329837%2Fmadurai-doctor-maruti-eco-ambulance-that-treats-elderly-people-with-disability-at-home-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20medical%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20coverage%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20year%20to%20all%20eligible%20senior%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20financial%20background.%20De