riticized%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20collaborating%20with%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections.%20AAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20demanded%20action%20against%20Congress%20leader%20Ajay%20Maken%20for%20his%20derogatory%20remarks%20about%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20AAP%20warned%20of%20potential%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20if%20Congress's%20actions%20do%20not%20align%20with%20their%20principles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20Are%20No%20Permanent%20Villains%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20Shyam%20Benegal%20Told%20Me%20About%20Bollywood's%20Bad%20Men%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Frbm9nms8_shyam-benegal_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShyam%20babu's%20number%3F%20Yes%2C%20I%20think%20I%20have%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Ziya%20us%20Salam%2C%20the%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu's%3C%2Fem%3E%20supplement%20%3Cem%3EMetroplus%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Delhi%2C%20in%20response%20to%20my%20request.%20This%20was%20sometime%20in%20June-July%202010%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20my%20three-year%20stint%20in%20Delhi-NCR.%20I%20was%20working%20on%20the%20manuscript%20of%20the%20non-fiction%20%3Cem%3EPure%20Evil%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Bad%20Men%20of%20Bollywood%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Harper%20Collins)%20and%20needed%20to%20interview%20leading%20filmmakers%20and%20actors%20as%20part%20of%20my%20research.%20I%20got%20through%20to%20Shyam%20Benegal%20and%20received%20his%20first%20blessing%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20Delhi%20this%20week.%20You%20can%20meet%20me%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20saving%20me%20the%20cost%20of%20travelling%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20book%20%3Cem%3ERD%20Burman%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Music%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20still%20undergoing%20edits%20and%20the%20release%20was%20a%20year%20away%2C%20I%20was%20not%20a%20published%20author%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20freelancer%20for%20Metroplus%20and%20am%20co-authoring%20my%20first%20book%20on%20RD%20Burman.%20And%20I%20am%20writing%20one%20more%20on%20the%20grey%20shades%20of%20characters%20in%20Bollywood%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20only%20truthful%20introduction%20possible%20when%20I%20entered%20his%20study.%20The%20choice%20of%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cgrey%20shades%E2%80%9D%20was%20deliberate%20as%20I%20needed%20his%20wisdom%20on%20a%20specific%20section%20on%20the%20ambiguous%20characters%20of%20Hindi%20cinema.%20I%20pressed%20the%20%E2%80%98Record'%20button%20on%20my%20portable%20Sony%20cassette%20recorder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Villains%20Evolved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20face%20of%20villains%20has%20been%20changing%20for%20the%20last%2060%20years.%20Do%20you%20believe%20it%20has%20represented%20the%20changing%20society%3F%E2%80%9D%20was%20my%20first%20question.%20%E2%80%9COf%20course%20it%20has%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%E2%80%98Professor'%20began.%20The%20student%20sat%20up%20attentively.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20kind%20of%20performing%20art%20has%20a%20long%20history%20and%20has%20had%20a%20moral%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20story%20because%20it's%20very%20closely%20tied%20to%20the%20way%20we%20live%20and%20the%20ideas%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20inculcate.%20In%20our%20films%2C%20too%2C%20we%20designed%20our%20villains%20likewise%20because%20that%20is%20part%20of%20our%20tradition.%20A%20hundred%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20we%20started%20to%20make%20our%20own%20films%2C%20we%20took%20everything%20lock%20stock%20and%20barrel%20from%20our%20earlier%20entertainment%20traditions%20and%20from%20the%20West.%20But%20since%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20the%20whole%20definition%20of%20heroes%20and%20villains%20has%20changed.%20Now%20you're%20looking%20at%20people%20as%20human%20beings%20in%20various%20shades%20of%20grey.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20had%20a%20clear%20morality%20tale.%20But%20now%2C%20we%20are%20shifting%20gears%20from%20the%20Ramayana%20kind%20of%20morality%20tale%20of%20shining%20goodness%20to%20a%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20a%20more%20complex%2C%20a%20more%20difficult%20morality%20tale%20of%20Mahabharata.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20sir%2C%20from%20%3Cem%3EKismet%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1943)%20itself%2C%20haven't%20there%20been%20anti-heroes%20in%20every%20other%20decade%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20student%20questioned%20respectfully.%20Clarified%20Benegal%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20study%20those%20films%2C%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20so%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20so.%20Eventually%20in%20%3Cem%3EKismet%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EAwara%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1951)%2C%20the%20hero%20is%20still%20the%20shining%20good%20man.%20It%20is%20only%20in%20the%20last%2030-40%20years%20that%20Indian%20audiences%20have%20come%20to%20accept%20a%20much%20more%20sophisticated%20rendition%20of%20characters%20and%20an%20acceptance%20of%20people%20without%20labelling%20them%20immoral.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20or%20Dibakar%20Banerjee's%20films%2C%20the%20characters%20are%20amoral%20and%20not%20immoral%3B%20for%20example%20in%20%3Cem%3EDev%20D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2009)%2C%20he%20is%20amoral%2C%20not%20immoral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20poster%20of%20the%20movie%20Kismet%2C%20featuring%20Ashok%20Kumar%20and%20Mumtaz%20Shanti%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20poster%20of%20the%20movie%20Kismet%2C%20featuring%20Ashok%20Kumar%20and%20Mumtaz%20Shanti%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsb4tit8_kismet_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20poster%20of%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EKismet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20Ashok%20Kumar%20and%20Mumtaz%20Shanti%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%20that%20moment%20I%20learnt%20something%20new%E2%80%94the%20nuances%20of%20the%20two%20words%20in%20the%20context%20of%20films.%20But%20I%20was%20still%20searching%20for%20that%20central%20idea%20of%20anti-heroes.%20Benegal%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20early%2070s%2C%20there%20was%20also%20this%20American%20film%3Cem%3E%20Dirty%20Harry%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20defined%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20hero%2Fanti-hero%20(which%20came%20into%20Amitabh%20Bachchan's%20%3Cem%3EZanjeer%3C%2Fem%3E)%20who%20used%20the%20methods%20of%20evil%20men%20to%20destroy%20evil.%20That%20came%20to%20stay.%20The%20evil%20person%20himself%20did%20not%20need%20any%20fresh%20definition.%20He%20remained%20a%20villain.%20But%20the%20hero%20was%20shifting.%20He%20had%20grey%20characters.%20Hitherto%2C%20the%20heroes%20were%20all%20unblemished%20ones.%20But%20now%20the%20hero%20was%20not%20the%20totally%20morally%2C%20unblemished%20hero%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fig55n5qg_zanjeer_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EAmitabh%20Bacchan%20in%20%3Cem%3EZanjeer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20are%20you%20saying%20that%20the%20anti-hero%20is%20the%20person%20with%20good%20intentions%3F%20Then%20who%20is%20the%20villain%3F%20Is%20he%20the%20bad%20guy%20with%20a%20bad%20motive%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20sought%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20original%20heroes%20followed%20the%20Gandhi%20way%2C%20the%20right%20way.%20That's%20a%20typical%20hero%E2%80%94right%20ends%20by%20right%20means.%20To%20get%20to%20the%20right%20ends%20by%20any%20means%E2%80%94that%20is%20anti-hero%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20And%20that%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98Aha!'%20moment.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20got%20the%20peg%20for%20my%20anti-heroes%20section%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98The%20differentiator%20between%20a%20villain%20and%20an%20anti-hero%20is%20in%20the%20motive.%20The%20villain%20has%20a%20bad%20motive.%20The%20anti-hero%20has%20a%20good%20motive%20with%20improper%20means%20to%20achieve%20it.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20discussion%20on%20grey%20shades%20of%20characters%20would%20be%20complete%20without%20us%20speaking%20about%20his%20masterpiece%20%3Cem%3EKalyug%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1981)%3F%20Benegal%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20villain%20in%20%3Cem%3EKalyug%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20even%20Dhanraj%20who%20played%20Duryodhana.%20He%20was%20justified%20in%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20as%20he%20felt%20that%20he%20had%20far%20greater%20legal%20rights%20to%20the%20business.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20who%20had%20created%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20Karna%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplained%20Benegal%2C%20%E2%80%9CKaran%20Singh%20(the%20equivalent%20of%20Karna%20in%20%3Cem%3EKalyug%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20the%20most%20interesting%20character.%20He%20finds%20himself%20on%20the%20wrong%20side.%20But%20his%20loyalty%20for%20Dhanraj%20(the%20modern%20version%20of%20Duryodhana%20in%20%3Cem%3EKalyug%3C%2Fem%3E)%20gave%20him%20his%20identity%20and%20acceptance%2C%20which%20even%20his%20mother%20didn't.%20And%20the%20complexity%20came%20when%20Karan%20Singh%20found%20out%20that%20he%20was%20the%20eldest%20of%20the%20Puranchand%20family%20(equivalent%20of%20the%20Pandavas)%2C%20and%20this%20fact%20was%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20with%20his%20loyalty%20to%20Dhanraj%2C%20the%20rival%20of%20the%20Puranchand%20family.%20Karan%20suffered%20neglect%20all%20his%20life%20and%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20trickery%20by%20Bharat%20(equivalent%20of%20Arjuna)%20of%20the%20Puranchand%20family.%20Karan%20was%20not%20at%20all%20a%20villain.%20He%20was%20the%20tragic%20hero.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fggv5fn5_kal-yug_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EShashi%20Kapoor%20and%20Amrish%20Puri%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKalyug%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20please%20give%20me%20a%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20apologised.%20I%20rewound%20the%20cassette%20recorder%20and%20replayed%20the%20last%2020%20seconds%20to%20check%20for%20any%20malfunction%20in%20the%20recording.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Karan%20was%20not%20at%20all%20a%20villain.%20He%20was%20the%20tragic%20hero%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20played.%20All%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20sir%2C%20my%20next%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20films%2C%20we%20discussed%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnkur%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ENishant%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EJunoon%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EBhumika%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20few%20pearls%20of%20wisdom%20were%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20Surya%20in%20%3Cem%3EAnkur%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewent%20through%20in%20school%20and%20college%20was%20the%20acceptance%20of%20feudal%20relationships%3B%20that%20he%20was%20the%20boss%20and%20others%20were%20his%20slaves.%20But%20even%20in%20a%20master-slave%20relationship%2C%20you're%20responsible%20for%20the%20slave%20because%20there%20is%20a%20human%20relationship%20as%20well.%20But%20he%20falls%20into%20the%20pattern%20and%20then%20he%20cannot%20take%20the%20responsibility.%20Therefore%2C%20willy-nilly%2C%20he%20becomes%20a%20villain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20me.%20About%20%3Cem%3ENishant%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20landlord%20brothers%20could%20do%20exactly%20what%20they%20wanted.%20But%20Sushila%20recognises%20her%20own%20sexuality%20(even%20though%20she%20has%20been%20raped)%20and%20her%20own%20love%20for%20the%20young%20man%20who%20acts%20eventually%20as%20her%20saviour%20(Vishwam%2C%20the%20youngest%20landlord).%20It%20is%20a%20very%20complex%20idea.%20No%20characters%20like%20these%20were%20ever%20created%20in%20Hindi%20cinema.%20Sushila%20was%20conscious%20of%20her%20own%20sexual%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0sms6ebo_ankur_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EAnant%20Nag%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20in%20%3Cem%3EAnkur%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20could%20sense%20that%20we%20were%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20hour%20assigned%20to%20me.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20what%20is%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Hindi%20cinema%20villain%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20permanent%20villain%20or%20a%20permanent%20hero.%20It%20will%20depend%20on%20situations.%20Circumstances%20change.%20With%20the%20shift%20of%20the%20positions%20of%20people%2C%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20villains%20or%20heroes.%20IPL%20is%20an%20example.%20In%20the%20first%20three%20IPLs%2C%20everybody%20saw%20Lalit%20Modi%20as%20a%20brilliant%20marketing%20strategist%20who%20delivered%20the%20most%20brilliant%20entertainment%20coup%20of%20all%20time.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20worst%20villain%20you%20could%20possibly%20see.%20Things%20are%20constantly%20moving.%20This%20is%20how%20perceptions%20change.%20These%20are%20things%20that%20constantly%20go%20through%20the%20minds%20of%20us%20filmmakers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shyam%20Benegal%20summed%20up.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20took%20his%20blessings%20and%20left%2C%20filled%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20ligh