%20whale%20researchers%2C%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20calf's%20health%20based%20on%20the%20behavior%20of%20both%20J35%20and%20J61.%20Early%20life%20is%20always%20dangerous%20for%20new%20calves%2C%20with%20a%20very%20high%20mortality%20rate%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20J35%20is%20an%20experienced%20mother%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20she%20is%20able%20to%20keep%20J61%20alive%20through%20these%20difficult%20early%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMichael%20Weiss%2C%20research%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Whale%20Research%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20researchers%20were%20initially%20not%20able%20to%20confirm%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20calf%2C%20but%20after%20observing%20it%20%E2%80%9Cconfidently%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20assigned%20Tahlequah%20as%20the%20mother%20and%20the%20baby%20as%20alpha-numeric%20J61.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20nature%20enthusiast%20and%20photographer%2C%20who%20captured%20the%20calf%2C%20said%20he%20was%20shocked%20after%20seeing%20the%20calf.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20looking%20through%20my%20photos%20to%20see%20who%20the%20whales%20were%20that%20passed%20close%20to%20the%20port%20side%20of%20the%20ferry%20I%20was%20on%20and%20noticed%20a%20much%20smaller%20dorsal%20on%20one%20of%20the%20photos.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20scrolling%20through%20the%20series%2C%20the%20photographer%20realised%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20very%20tiny%20calf%2C%20much%20smaller%20than%20any%20of%20the%20known%20young%20ones%20in%20the%20group.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTahlequah%2C%20or%20J35%2C%20made%20headlines%20six%20years%20ago%20after%20she%20swam%20with%20the%20body%20of%20her%20calf%20for%20about%201%2C000%20miles%20of%20ocean.%20The%20calf%20had%20died%20within%20hours%20of%20birth.%20She%20swam%20with%20the%20body%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20sinking.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTwo%20years%20later%2C%20she%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20first%20known%20baby%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20J57%2C%20in%202020.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20mother%20of%20another%20orca%20named%20J47.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735199040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fo52102a_orca-tahlequah-facebook_625x300_26_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftahlequah-orca-who-carried-her-dead-calf-for-1-600-km-welcomes-a-new-baby-7334515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20orca%2C%20who%20carried%20her%20dead%20calf%20for%2017%20days%20and%20swam%20over%201600%20kmof%20ocean%20in%202018%2C%20has%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20new%20baby%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Center%20for%20Whale%20Research.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftahlequah-orca-who-carried-her-dead-calf-for-1-600-km-welcomes-a-new-baby-7334515%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Come%20To%20Morgue%2C%20Stand%20For%2010%20Mins%3A%20Chinese%20Funeral%20Home's%20Post%20For%20Jobseekers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20funeral%20home%20in%20Rushan%2C%20Shandong%20province%2C%20China%2C%20is%20hiring%20a%20%26quot%3Bmorgue%20manager%26quot%3B%2C%20offering%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%202%2C200%20yuan%20(Rs%2025%2C000).%20Sounds%20simple%3F%20Wait%20till%20you%20read%20the%20fine%20print.%20The%20job%20requires%20candidates%20to%20endure%2010%20minutes%20in%20a%20freezing%20morgue%20to%20qualify%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20unconventional%20test%20were%20shared%20on%20December%2011%20by%20an%20internet%20user%20from%20Rushan.%20The%20hiring%20process%2C%20conducted%20by%20Rushan%20Xinmike%20Human%20Resources%20Co.%2C%20Ltd.%2C%20was%20advertised%20by%20the%20Rushan%20Municipal%20Bureau%20of%20Human%20Resources%20and%20Social%20Security%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplicants%20must%20meet%20specific%20criteria%2C%20including%20permanent%20household%20registration%20in%20Rushan%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20work%2024-hour%20shifts%2C%20male%2C%20age%20below%2045%2C%20and%20at%20least%20a%20junior%20secondary%20school%20education%2C%20the%20SCMP%20reported.%20Candidates%20must%20also%20pay%20a%2070%20yuan%20(Rs%20816)%20exam%20fee%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%2C%20a%20three-year%20contract%2C%20includes%20various%20evaluation%20stages%20such%20as%20the%20morgue%20room%20test%2C%20structured%20interviews%2C%20background%20checks%2C%20medical%20exams%2C%20and%20a%20six-month%20probation%20period.%20However%2C%20the%20role%20does%20not%20offer%20%26quot%3Bbian%20zhi%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20benefit%20that%20guarantees%20stable%2C%20lifelong%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rushan%20Funeral%20Services%20Centre%20representative%20explained%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20morgue%20test.%20%26quot%3BThe%20special%20requirement%20is%20just%20a%20test%20method%20because%20some%20people%20have%20strong%20taboos%20or%20fears%20staying%20too%20long%20in%20such%20settings%2C%20but%20our%20work%20requires%20someone%20who%20can%20remain%20in%20the%20room%20for%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20Eastern%20Business%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%2C%20however%2C%20questioned%20the%20ethics%20of%20the%20hiring%20process.%20Wang%2C%20a%20funeral%20home%20management%20professional%20in%20southwestern%20China%2C%20called%20the%20test%20inappropriate%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20on-site%20test%20might%20assess%20a%20candidate's%20psychological%20resilience%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20unethical.%20Professional%20psychological%20tests%20or%20internships%20would%20be%20better%20alternatives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20concerns%2C%20China's%20funeral%20services%20market%20continues%20to%20expand%2C%20growing%20from%20169.5%20billion%20yuan%20in%202015%20to%20310.2%20billion%20yuan%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Zhiyan%20Consultin