%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fdelhi-ncr-sees-highest-yearly-jump-of-30-in-home-prices-in-2024-124122600374_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20has%20recorded%20the%20highest%20yearly%20jump%20in%20home%20prices%2C%20showing%20a%20remarkable%2030%25%20increase%20from%20Q4%202023%20to%20Q4%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fdelhi-ncr-sees-highest-yearly-jump-of-30-in-home-prices-in-2024-124122600374_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonu%20Sood%20Was%20Offered%20Chief%20Minister%20Post.%20He%20Refused%20Because...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Sonu%20Sood%2C%20who%20gained%20a%20big%20fan%20following%20by%20helping%20migrant%20workers%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20recently%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20offered%20posts%20such%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20and%20a%20seat%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20However%2C%20he%20refused%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20offered%20the%20position%20of%20chief%20minister.%20When%20I%20refused%2C%20they%20told%20me%20to%20become%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20These%20were%20very%20big%20people%20in%20the%20country%20who%20also%20offered%20me%20a%20seat%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20They%20told%20me%20to%20take%20it%20and%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20fight%20for%20anything%20in%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sood%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Humans%20of%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20exciting%20phase%20when%20such%20powerful%20people%20want%20to%20meet%20you%20and%20encourage%20you%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20politics%20as%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Blose%