ws%2Fkartik-aaryan-proves-he-is-a-pushpa-2-fan-as-he-mimics-allu-arjuns-iconic-style%2Farticleshow%2F116672226.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Warren%20Buffett%20Plans%20To%20Distribute%20His%20Fortune%20After%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Warren%20Buffett%20has%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20future%20of%20his%20immense%20fortune%20and%20offered%20advice%20on%20inheritance%20in%20a%20message%20to%20his%20company's%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20CEO%20revealed%20his%20plans%20for%20wealth%20distribution%20in%20a%20letter%20posted%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F12%2F25%2Fbusiness%2Fbuffett-talks-mortality-and-philanthropy-in-surprise-shareholder-letter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Buffett%20announced%20that%20%241.1%20billion%20of%20his%20Berkshire%20shares%20would%20be%20donated%20to%20his%20family's%20four%20foundations%2C%20with%20the%20remainder%20of%20his%20holdings%20to%20be%20gradually%20distributed%20by%20his%20three%20children%20after%20his%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2094-year-old's%20message%20carried%20an%20introspective%20tone%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20inevitability%20of%20mortality.%20%E2%80%9CFather%20time%20always%20wins.%20But%20he%20can%20be%20fickle%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20unfair%20and%20even%20cruel%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20ending%20life%20at%20birth%20or%20soon%20thereafter%20while%2C%20at%20other%20times%2C%20waiting%20a%20century%20or%20so%20before%20paying%20a%20visit.%20To%20date%2C%20I've%20been%20very%20lucky%2C%20but%2C%20before%20long%2C%20he%20will%20get%20around%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20challenges%20his%20children%20may%20face%20due%20to%20their%20own%20advancing%20years%20%E2%80%94%20now%20aged%2071%2C%2069%20and%2066%20%E2%80%94%20Mr%20Buffett%20said%20that%20he%20has%20appointed%20three%20potential%20trustees%20to%20ensure%20his%20wishes%20are%20honoured%20if%20his%20children%20cannot%20complete%20the%20task.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20potential%20successor%20trustees%20have%20been%20designated.%20Each%20is%20well%20known%20to%20my%20children%20and%20makes%20sense%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20They%20are%20also%20somewhat%20younger%20than%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Buffett%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underscored%20his%20preference%20for%20decisions%20within%20the%20foundations%20to%20be%20made%20unanimously%20and%20shared%20his%20approach%20to%20simplifying%20his%20will%2C%20which%20he%20reviews%20periodically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Buffett%20also%20offered%20advice%20for%20parents%20navigating%20the%20sensitive%20topic%20of%20inheritance%20planning.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20one%20further%20suggestion%20for%20all%20parents%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20of%20modest%20or%20staggering%20wealth.%20When%20your%20children%20are%20mature%2C%20have%20them%20read%20your%20will%20before%20you%20sign%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20transparency%2C%20urging%20parents%20to%20explain%20their%20decisions%20to%20avoid%20misunderstandings.%20%E2%80%9CBe%20sure%20each%20child%20understands%20both%20the%20logic%20for%20your%20decisions%20and%20the%20responsibilities%20they%20will%20encounter%20upon%20your%20death.%20If%20any%20have%20questions%20or%20suggestions%2C%20listen%20carefully%20and%20adopt%20those%20found%20sensible.%20You%20don't%20want%20your%20children%20asking%20%E2%80%9CWhy%3F%E2%80%9D%20in%20respect%20to%20testamentary%20decisions%20when%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20respond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20decades%20of%20observation%2C%20Mr%20Buffett%20noted%20how%20unresolved%20issues%20stemming%20from%20wills%20have%20caused%20discord%20among%20families.%20He%20recounted%20instances%20he%20and%20his%20late%20busin