lish%20good%20governance%20here.%20Immense%20work%20was%20done%20between%202005%20and%202010%20to%20rid%20Bihar%20of%20jungle%20raj.%20The%20NDA%20government%20under%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20leadership%20has%20freed%20Bihar%20from%20the%20jungle%20raj%20of%20kidnappings%2C%20murders%2C%20loot%20and%20rapes.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNDA's%20government%20will%20be%20formed%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed%2C%20a%20framed%20photograph%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20the%20wall%20behind%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister's%20remark%20and%20then%20the%20clarification%20is%20also%20significant%20because%20the%20main%20Opposition%20RJD%20has%20repeatedly%20stressed%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20controlling%20the%20Bihar%20government%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20little%20control%20over%20the%20state%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735190160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fctvkvpho_vijay-kumar-sinha_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-vijay-kumar-sinha-bihar-deputy-chief-ministers-tribute-to-ab-vajpayee-then-a-clarification-7333784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20no-holds-barred%20speech%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20late%20Atal%20Bihar%20Vajpayee%20landed%20Bihar%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Sinha%20in%20trouble%20yesterday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-vijay-kumar-sinha-bihar-deputy-chief-ministers-tribute-to-ab-vajpayee-then-a-clarification-7333784%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20To%20Build%20World's%20Largest%20Hydropower%20Dam%20In%20Tibet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20approved%20the%20construction%20of%20what%20will%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20hydropower%20dam%2C%20kicking%20off%20an%20ambitious%20project%20on%20the%20eastern%20rim%20of%20the%20Tibetan%20plateau%20that%20could%20affect%20millions%20downstream%20in%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dam%2C%20which%20will%20be%20located%20in%20the%20lower%20reaches%20of%20the%20Yarlung%20Zangbo%20River%2C%20could%20produce%20300%20billion%20kilowatt-hours%20of%20electricity%20annually%2C%20according%20to%20an%20estimate%20provided%20by%20the%20Power%20Construction%20Corp%20of%20China%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20more%20than%20triple%20the%2088.2%20billion%20kWh%20designed%20capacity%20of%20the%20Three%20Gorges%20Dam%2C%20currently%20the%20world's%20largest%2C%20in%20central%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20will%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20meeting%20China's%20carbon%20peaking%20and%20carbon%20neutrality%20goals%2C%20stimulate%20related%20industries%20such%20as%20engineering%2C%20and%20create%20jobs%20in%20Tibet%2C%20the%20official%20Xinhua%20news%20agency%20reported%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20Yarlung%20Zangbo%20falls%20a%20dramatic%202%2C000%20metres%20(6%2C561%20feet)%20within%20a%20short%20span%20of%2050%20km%20(31%20miles)%2C%20offering%20huge%20hydropower%20potential%20as%20well%20as%20unique%20engineering%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlay%20for%20building%20the%20dam%2C%20including%20engineering%20costs%2C%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20eclipse%20the%20Three%20Gorges%20dam%2C%20which%20cost%20254.2%20billion%20yuan(%2434.83%20billion).%20This%20included%20the%20resettling%20of%20the%201.4%20million%20people%20it%20displaced%20and%20was%20more%20than%20four%20times%20the%20initial%20estimate%20of%2057%20billion%20yuan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20not%20indicated%20how%20many%20people%20the%20Tibet%20project%20would%20displace%20and%20how%20it%20would%20affect%20the%20local%20ecosystem%2C%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20and%20most%20diverse%20on%20the%20plateau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20Chinese%20officials%2C%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20Tibet%2C%20which%20they%20say%20hold%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20China's%20hydroelectric%20power%20potential%2C%20would%20not%20have%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%20or%20on%20downstream%20water%20supplies%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20nevertheless%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20dam%2C%20with%20the%20project%20potentially%20altering%20not%20only%20the%20local%20ecology%20but%20also%20the%20flow%20and%20course%20of%20the%20river%20downstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yarlung%20Zangbo%20becomes%20the%20Brahmaputra%20river%20as%20it%20leaves%20Tibet%20and%20flows%20south%20into%20India's%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20states%20and%20finally%20into%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20already%20commenced%20hydropower%20generation%20on%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20the%20Yarlung%20Zangbo%2C%20which%20flows%20from%20the%20west%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Tibet.%20It%20is%20planning%20more%20projects%20upstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735189980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Ffgvd8cno_dam-genericpixabay-_625x300_30_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-to-build-worlds-largest-hydropower-dam-in-tibet-7333718%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20approved%20the%20construction%20of%20what%20will%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20hydropower%20dam%2C%20kicking%20off%20an%20ambitious%20project%20on%20the%20eastern%20rim%20of%20the%20Tibetan%20plateau%20that%20could%20affect%20millions%20downstream%20in%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworl