here%20they%20could%20channel%20all%20of%20their%20creative%2C%20academic%2C%20and%20artistic%20visions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20shares.%20The%20students%20also%20created%20lasting%20traditions%2C%20like%20planting%20trees%20each%20year.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20come%20to%20Niwant%2C%20the%20whole%20gully%20is%20green%20because%20every%20year%2C%20the%2012th-grade%20batch%20plants%20trees%20to%20their%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spirit%20of%20giving%20back%20is%20ingrained%20in%20Niwant%E2%80%99s%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20had%20%E2%80%98The%201%25%20Club%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20by%20some%20ex-students%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20shares.%20Former%20students%20have%20started%20their%20own%20Niwants%20in%20local%20communities%2C%20continuing%20the%20legacy.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20house%20some%20of%20the%20students%20who%20study%20at%20Niwant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20proudly%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETowards%20a%20future%20with%20no%20scribes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Meera%20Badve%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20along%20with%20their%20daughter%20Uma%2C%20launched%20%3Cem%3ESwalekhan%20Typing%20Tutor%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20multilingual%20typing%20tutor%20app%20designed%20to%20help%20visually%20impaired%20students%20write%20their%20exams%20independently.%20Uma%2C%20who%20has%20a%20diverse%20professional%20background%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20for%20the%20visually%20impaired%20came%20to%20me%20very%20naturally%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20just%20what%20I%20grew%20around.%E2%80%9D%20Raised%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20visually%20impaired%20students%20were%20always%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20Uma%20understood%20the%20struggles%20they%20faced.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wrote%20so%20many%20papers%20for%20these%20kids%20as%20a%20scribe%2C%20and%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20completely%20meritorious%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwalekhan%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20eliminate%20the%20dependence%20on%20scribes%20during%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visually%20impaired%20community%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20strides%20in%20terms%20of%20becoming%20independent%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20giving%20exams%2C%20they%20still%20depend%20on%20scribes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20says.%20Initially%2C%20they%20hoped%20the%20app%20would%20be%20widely%20adopted%20by%20older%20students%20in%20colleges%2C%20but%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20older%20students%20had%20become%20so%20dependent%20on%20scribes%20that%20they%20had%20acute%20anxiety%20on%20giving%20them%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20reflects.%20So%2C%20they%20shifted%20focus%20to%20younger%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20student%20using%20the%20app%20to%20type%20in%20Marathi%20independently%20without%20a%20scribe.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNiwantPune-143_11zon-1734329947-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-389486%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20eight%20months%2C%201%2C200%20children%20across%20Maharashtra%20learned%20to%20type%20in%20Marathi%20using%20the%20Swalekhan%20app.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20partnered%20with%20some%20blind%20schools%20in%20Pune%20and%20taught%20Class%204%20to%20Class%208%20children%20how%20to%20understand%20audio%20instructions%20and%20type%20without%20a%20scribe%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20shares.%20In%20just%20eight%20months%2C%20they%20taught%201%2C200%20children%20across%20Maharashtra%20how%20to%20type%20in%20Marathi.%20The%20app%20is%20now%20being%20used%20by%20over%202%2C000%20children%2C%20with%20around%20150%20taking%20their%20exams%20independently%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20government%20support%2C%20the%20app%20has%20expanded%20its%20reach%2C%20including%20a%20Hindi%20version%20and%20plans%20to%20integrate%20it%20into%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Intelligence.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20West%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20a%20scribe.%20They%20teach%20touch%20typing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20adds.%20Through%20Swalekhan%2C%20Niwant%20is%20now%20helping%20reshape%20the%20future%20of%20visually%20impaired%20students%20in%20India%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20education%20without%20relying%20on%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiwant%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20intertwined%20with%20the%20Badve%20family%E2%80%99s%20dedication.%20Uma%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20dad%20turned%2060%2C%20he%20left%20his%20business%20and%20joined%20my%20mother.%20The%20number%20of%20students%20we%20had%20coming%20in%20grew%2C%20so%20it%20was%20good%20that%20along%20with%20the%20volunteers%20and%20teachers%2C%20she%20had%20more%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeera%20and%20her%20husband%20started%20by%20providing%20basic%20education%20and%20braille%20resources%20and%20then%20expanded%20to%20include%20classes%20for%20competitive%20exams%2C%20like%20banking%20and%20government%20jobs.%20Over%20200%20Niwant%20students%20are%20now%20employed%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20banking%20sector%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20quota%20for%20the%20visually%20impaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Miles%20to%20go%20before%20I%20sleep%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiwant%E2%80%99s%20unique%20model%20of%20learning%20and%20support%20has%20led%20to%20lasting%20relationships%20among%20its%20students.%20%E2%80%9CKids%20were%20coming%20in%20at%2011th%20grade%2C%20and%20we%20would%20help%20them%20until%20they%20got%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20explains.%20Many%20students%2C%20who%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20Niwant%20for%20years%2C%20ended%20up%20marrying%20one%20another.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20only%20child%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wanted%20siblings.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20had%20a%20big%20family%20of%20visually%20impaired%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329201%2Fgrailmaker-innovations-vision-nanny-platform-app-solution-for-kids-cortical-visual-impairment%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20Vision%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20software%20company%20that%20started%20as%20part%20of%20Niwant%2C%20is%20another%20example%20of%20the%20impact%20Niwant%20has%20had.%20%E2%80%9CSiddhant%20Chothe%2C%20one%20of%20our%20students%20who%20lost%20his%20vision%20later%20in%20life%2C%20was%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20job%20despite%20having%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20computer%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20unsuccessful%20attempts%20at%20getting%20Siddhant%20a%20job%2C%20the%20Niwant%20family%2C%20realising%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20anyone%20else%2C%20decided%20to%20start%20something%20of%20their%20own.%20With%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20Siddharth%20launched%20Tech%20Vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C