roduce%20at%20fair%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20champion%20both%20the%20exceptional%20products%20these%20farmers%20create%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270093%2Fpeanut-jaggery-health-benefits-indian-food-recipe-for-chikki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20proteins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20through%20our%20peanut%20butters%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUplifting%20rural%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20their%20primary%20processing%20units%2C%20Aman%20started%20purchasing%20the%20processed%20groundnuts%20at%20Rs%20100-120%20per%20kilogram%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20prices%20they%20were%20getting.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20primary%20processing%20is%20now%20done%20by%20these%20farmers%2C%20they%20also%20have%20their%20own%20seeds%20to%20put%20back%20into%20harvesting%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20Aman%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20could%20all%20work%20together%20for%20better%20profits.%20He%20brought%20us%20seeds%20and%20we%20worked%20on%20figuring%20out%20the%20best%20farming%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20our%20soil%20tested.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20was%20something%20you%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20do.%20Checking%20and%20regulating%20the%20pH%20levels%2C%20nitrogen%20phosphate%2C%20and%20carbon%2016%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20any%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20scientific%20perspective%2C%20Aman%20connected%20them%20with%20Dr%20Kishan%20Chandra%2C%20a%20scientist%20specialising%20in%